  "texts": [
    "Steiner's team validated the platform by synthesizing three well-known drugs (diphenhydramine hydrochloride, rufinamide, and sildenafil) without any human intervention.",
    "The purity and yield of these drugs were found to be similar to, or even better than, those synthesized using classical methods.",
    "This tool has the potential to automate the entire chemical synthesis process, and therefore speed up the drug production phase.",
    "The programming of this tool requires expertise in a chemical mark-up language called extensible markup language-based domain-specific language.",
    "After manufacturing, the target is to advertise the drug."
